411
01:09:21,880 --> 01:09:48,439
[SPEAKER_00] On izvuče iz Evanđelja dana neku parolu, koja je poticaj tog dana, znači baciše mreže i pođeše za njim, znači onda na tu tezu se radi podjela svog nekog perioda, neko, ono, uvijek obavezno je to, neko od dečki se digne i podijeli svoj period,

412
01:09:48,439 --> 01:10:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji, ono, živi, kak živi, koji ima poteškoće, koga loše živi, s kim loše živi, koga je pitao oprost, kome je kaj zamjerio i tako, ono, to se, ono, priča skroz otvoreno.

413
01:10:06,760 --> 01:10:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga je doručak i onda se ide u radni, radne sati do, do ručka, ručak 12, poslije ručka je...

414
01:10:18,079 --> 01:10:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] Prosij daj mi neke poslove.

415
01:10:19,199 --> 01:10:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] Stolarija, štala, lavanderija, vrt.

416
01:10:29,439 --> 01:10:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] Inači, kaj zajednica je u stvari samo, samo održivo.

417
01:10:32,380 --> 01:10:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] Samo održivo, tako.

418
01:10:33,539 --> 01:10:33,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

419
01:10:33,720 --> 01:10:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, svaka bratoština ima stoku, ima stolariju, ima bravariju, ima mehaniku, ima sirnicu, ima...

420
01:10:48,760 --> 01:10:54,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo, pizzu, to je spekaru.

421
01:10:54,319 --> 01:10:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] I predznanje nije potrebno, oći to je ovo.

422
01:10:57,039 --> 01:10:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, pa sve naučiš.

423
01:10:58,420 --> 01:11:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ti, ono, i tak se prenaša se znanje sa, ono, ja sam tam svašto naučio, od tih poslova.

424
01:11:05,260 --> 01:11:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Od mužnje krava, rađenje sire.

425
01:11:07,659 --> 01:11:08,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kje ti je bilo najbolje?

426
01:11:08,260 --> 01:11:10,399
[SPEAKER_00] Vrt.

427
01:11:10,399 --> 01:11:11,520
[SPEAKER_00] Vrt, dobro.

428
01:11:11,520 --> 01:11:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

429
01:11:11,840 --> 01:11:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] Sadnje, ono, naši, od malog sjemenčića da plodu, a to je baš, ono, lijepo i...

430
01:11:18,739 --> 01:11:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] I to mi je bilo super i poslije toga sam vodio kuhinju i cijelu, ajmo reći, svim bratovičnim...

431
01:11:28,600 --> 01:11:30,020
[SPEAKER_01] Jer tu si imao iskustva, u stvari.

432
01:11:30,020 --> 01:11:31,279
[SPEAKER_01] Tu si imao iskustva.

433
01:11:31,279 --> 01:11:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali ti, najjače je to da ti u početcima ne radiš to kaj ti znaš raditi, nego ono kaj ne znaš, raditi kaj ti se ne da.

434
01:11:38,079 --> 01:11:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nisam ja išao odmah u kuhinju, jer sam tu imao nekog iskustva, je to.

435
01:11:42,600 --> 01:11:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo sam radio u stolariji, ono, na nekom, na nekoj kombinirciji, ono,

436
01:11:48,720 --> 01:11:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sve znam čavo, ne znam za.

437
01:11:51,119 --> 01:11:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] A tamo me stavili gdje je najviše čavla i gdje se radi, ono, to je nevjerovatno.

438
01:11:58,960 --> 01:12:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] A nikom nisam niš rekao.

439
01:12:00,560 --> 01:12:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sam rekao su, ono, čim sam ušao, ostavio stvari i prvo moje zadrženje sa Anđelom Čuvarom je stolarija.

440
01:12:09,260 --> 01:12:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on je bio u stolariji i tam smo radili, znači, stvarno ne znam za bi čavo.

441
01:12:16,079 --> 01:12:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, i dan danas mi to ne ide.

442
01:12:19,739 --> 01:12:27,779
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je ono, svaka bratošna je s vama održiva i to funkcionira super.

443
01:12:27,779 --> 01:12:34,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, znači, rekli smo, ide rad na ta radni period, do ručka predpostavljam.

444
01:12:35,420 --> 01:12:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, do ručka, onda imaš sad tipo slobodno, što znači da slobodno vrijeme u zajednici ti je uvijek podjela s nekim, komunikacija.

445
01:12:46,039 --> 01:12:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ti uvijek moraš imati nekog s kim pričaš poslije ručka.

446
01:12:50,640 --> 01:12:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mreš ti spavati.

447
01:12:51,779 --> 01:12:53,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, nema spavanja niti.

448
01:12:53,479 --> 01:12:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] U slobodno vrijeme ne mreš ti spavati.

449
01:12:54,800 --> 01:13:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš negdje sjesti na klupicu i to je to i uvijek moraš ići.

450
01:13:00,539 --> 01:13:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja ujutro kad se probudim, pita Marine, s kim pričaš poslije ručka.

451
01:13:05,960 --> 01:13:08,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kažeš s nikim, ja možemo, ti ja može.

452
01:13:08,399 --> 01:13:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ja pričam s ovim, ja moram ići tražiti nekog druga.

453
01:13:11,300 --> 01:13:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] I uvijek moraš biti u paru, nema nikada sam.

454
01:13:14,359 --> 01:13:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] I to se sve vidi, znači, uvijek se to vidi.

455
01:13:17,579 --> 01:13:24,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je sam i, znači, jak si ti ostao sam i jak si, ono, bio malo pastrava, ribica lagano,

456
01:13:26,319 --> 01:13:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] doći će ti neko, kroz neko vrijeme, pozva te na stranu, imaš minutu da ti kaže zašto si bio sam,

457
01:13:32,760 --> 01:13:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] ovo, ono, ne možeš biti sam, šta se, ono, radiš, grbavi i tak dalje.

458
01:13:37,340 --> 01:13:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jako, dobro.

459
01:13:37,920 --> 01:13:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, to je, ono, super su to, to, ono, odlično napravljeno.

460
01:13:43,760 --> 01:13:46,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, znači, slobodno vrijeme je nakon ručka sat i pol.

461
01:13:46,180 --> 01:13:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda zvoni za popodnevni rad i popodnevni rad traje, ovisno o nekom dogovoru dana.

462
01:13:56,619 --> 01:14:02,939
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je taj dan misa ili je taj dan nekakva, ono, podjela života, jel?

463
01:14:02,939 --> 01:14:07,359
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je nešto što se radi u Bratovištini svakih 15 dana,

464
01:14:07,359 --> 01:14:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] kad se naprave grupe od tri, četiri dečka ili cure,

465
01:14:12,640 --> 01:14:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] gdje onda oni međusobno podijeljuju svoje, svoje poteškoće i onako kako žive

466
01:14:19,939 --> 01:14:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] i svaki od nas koji je u grupi, nas je sad tu, ne znam, nas dvoje,

467
01:14:25,819 --> 01:14:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] treba biti više od dvoje, svaki od nas podijeli svoj neki period

468
01:14:30,760 --> 01:14:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] i dobiješ obavezu, jel?

469
01:14:33,640 --> 01:14:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, obaveza ti je, znači, ja sam, ono, podijeljujem,

470
01:14:37,500 --> 01:14:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] nervozan sam, ovo, ispaljujem, ovo, to sam loše, tu, ovo,

471
01:14:42,039 --> 01:14:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] imam situaciju, ovako, imam to.

472
01:14:45,220 --> 01:14:51,479
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dobiješ ono, tipa, moram kontrolirati svoju prvu reakciju

473
01:14:51,479 --> 01:14:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] i kada sam to učinio u danu.

474
01:14:54,039 --> 01:14:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] I to svaku, nakon večere se te obaveze ispunje.

475
01:14:57,159 --> 01:14:58,020
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, vrlo mjerljivo.

476
01:14:58,020 --> 01:14:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

477
01:14:58,399 --> 01:14:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

478
01:14:59,039 --> 01:15:03,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si bio, ovaj, negdje prvi,

479
01:15:03,640 --> 01:15:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad si nekome otišao u susred reč da čini krivo,

480
01:15:08,239 --> 01:15:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] to je po meni najteže, jel, nekog u korit.

481
01:15:11,260 --> 01:15:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] To jest, znači, taj Elvira je nama uvijek pričala

482
01:15:15,840 --> 01:15:17,899
[SPEAKER_00] grijeh propusta je najveći grijeh.

483
01:15:17,899 --> 01:15:20,439
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vidiš da neko radi krivo, ti prođeš pored njega.

484
01:15:20,439 --> 01:15:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, i ne opamjeneš ga da, ono, radi krivo.

485
01:15:24,319 --> 01:15:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] znači činiš grijeh propusta.

486
01:15:25,779 --> 01:15:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je ona jako, jako je to strogo napravljeno.

487
01:15:29,500 --> 01:15:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] I to je, ono, super je to meni, meni bilo.

488
01:15:32,800 --> 01:15:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, evo, jako je, opet dajemu reći...

489
01:15:35,420 --> 01:15:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ti je mijao ljudima oko tebe nije.

490
01:15:36,840 --> 01:15:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] A nije ni meni, znači, nije, nije.

491
01:15:38,819 --> 01:15:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je teško otići, znači, jako je teško otići

492
01:15:41,319 --> 01:15:45,939
[SPEAKER_00] u susred nekom i reći, ono, ej, radiš krivo

493
01:15:45,939 --> 01:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] ili kako se to ponašaš ili kako to...

494
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,600
[SPEAKER_01] A lakše bi to u stvari primio od nekoga neg da...

495
01:15:50,600 --> 01:15:51,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, nego reći.

496
01:15:51,319 --> 01:15:54,560
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, znači, zavisi i od dana

497
01:15:54,560 --> 01:15:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] i radni dan završava u 6-7.

498
01:15:59,560 --> 01:16:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oko 7, pola 8 je večera.

499
01:16:05,000 --> 01:16:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] Prije toga nekako, ono, krunica.

500
01:16:09,180 --> 01:16:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ima jutarnja krunica, onda ima krunica

501
01:16:13,760 --> 01:16:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] na radnom mjestu, dok traje radno...

502
01:16:18,079 --> 01:16:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tepo, popadon, popodneni radni dio.

503
01:16:21,739 --> 01:16:25,859
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ima zadnja krunica,

504
01:16:25,859 --> 01:16:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] da li je ona šetajuća prije večere

505
01:16:30,119 --> 01:16:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili je u kapeli nakon večere,

506
01:16:33,079 --> 01:16:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] pa je još neki, ono, neka duhovna, ono, tema.

507
01:16:39,180 --> 01:16:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je to i u 9.30 ide u sobe

508
01:16:45,159 --> 01:16:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] i u 10.00 se ga svijetla i spasa.

509
01:16:47,239 --> 01:16:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, a kaj je ako se neko neće dići ujutro u 15.00 do 6.00?

510
01:16:52,619 --> 01:16:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja odlučim, ja odlučimo se spavati.

511
01:16:57,140 --> 01:16:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] Mora se digniti, ne može ne digniti se.

512
01:16:59,680 --> 01:17:00,640
[SPEAKER_00] Neko te digne.

513
01:17:00,640 --> 01:17:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ne moraš ići

514
01:17:03,119 --> 01:17:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] moliti krunicu,

515
01:17:04,760 --> 01:17:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali ideš raditi odmah u 15.00 do 6.00

516
01:17:07,420 --> 01:17:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to.

517
01:17:08,119 --> 01:17:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se moraš digniti.

518
01:17:09,960 --> 01:17:12,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, sad kad se rekao ne moraš moliti krunicu,

519
01:17:12,220 --> 01:17:14,060
[SPEAKER_01] je li uvijed za uću čenakolo,

520
01:17:14,060 --> 01:17:16,520
[SPEAKER_01] poprosti, kje opće znači čenakolo?

521
01:17:16,520 --> 01:17:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] Čenakolo je dvorana posljednje večere,

522
01:17:18,779 --> 01:17:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] ili tamo gdje su se apostoli sakrili

523
01:17:24,460 --> 01:17:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] dok nije došao do sveti.

524
01:17:27,239 --> 01:17:32,039
[SPEAKER_01] Je li nekakav uvijed za uću čenakolo da si vijednik?

525
01:17:32,039 --> 01:17:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] Može ući bilo ko.

526
01:17:34,500 --> 01:17:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo ko ima potrebu,

527
01:17:36,960 --> 01:17:38,439
[SPEAKER_00] može ući čenakolo bez obzira.

528
01:17:38,439 --> 01:17:40,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u...

529
01:17:40,439 --> 01:17:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, bilo je puno priča,

530
01:17:43,920 --> 01:17:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] znači i islamske vjeroispovijesti,

531
01:17:47,000 --> 01:17:50,319
[SPEAKER_00] protestantske vjeroispovijesti

532
01:17:50,319 --> 01:17:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] i ortodoksne...

533
01:17:54,920 --> 01:17:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pravoslavaca.

534
01:17:55,539 --> 01:17:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pravoslavaca, Makedonaca.

535
01:17:57,460 --> 01:17:58,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ali oni kao isto isprate normalno

536
01:17:58,859 --> 01:17:59,979
[SPEAKER_01] sada taj program ili...

537
01:17:59,979 --> 01:18:00,140
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

538
01:18:00,140 --> 01:18:00,939
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ok.

539
01:18:00,939 --> 01:18:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam, evo,

540
01:18:02,720 --> 01:18:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno doživio neka, ono,

541
01:18:05,220 --> 01:18:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] obraćenja sa islama na katoličanstvo

542
01:18:11,220 --> 01:18:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] i cijelih obitelji.

543
01:18:13,220 --> 01:18:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, pogotovo ljudi,

544
01:18:17,000 --> 01:18:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] u Kosovo.

545
01:18:17,760 --> 01:18:22,520
[SPEAKER_00] Moj jako dobar prijatelj je, ono,

546
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] se obratio, krstio,

547
01:18:25,079 --> 01:18:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] pričestio krizmo,

548
01:18:27,539 --> 01:18:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] njegovi roditelji

549
01:18:28,880 --> 01:18:32,359
[SPEAKER_00] i danas ti ljudi vode

550
01:18:32,359 --> 01:18:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] zajednicu u Prištini.

551
01:18:34,180 --> 01:18:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, znači,

552
01:18:36,159 --> 01:18:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] nije uvijek zavuć

553
01:18:37,239 --> 01:18:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] ko vjernik,

554
01:18:39,539 --> 01:18:41,979
[SPEAKER_01] a, jel ima puno ljudi

555
01:18:41,979 --> 01:18:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] koji izađuju iz černako,

556
01:18:43,720 --> 01:18:46,060
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisu vjernici ili...

557
01:18:46,060 --> 01:18:46,399
[SPEAKER_01] Supra.

558
01:18:50,000 --> 01:18:51,140
[SPEAKER_01] Zakaj to pitam.

559
01:18:51,140 --> 01:18:54,779
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim da je, u stvari,

560
01:18:54,779 --> 01:18:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] jako prožito po danu,

561
01:18:56,579 --> 01:18:59,020
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ta jedan fizički rad

562
01:18:59,020 --> 01:19:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] i duhovna ta komponenta.

563
01:19:02,119 --> 01:19:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] Je li može jedna bez druge,

564
01:19:05,619 --> 01:19:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] ili bi mogo reći,

565
01:19:06,739 --> 01:19:08,779
[SPEAKER_01] koja je važnija u tom procesu

566
01:19:08,779 --> 01:19:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji tamo dečki prolaze?

567
01:19:11,699 --> 01:19:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, ne može jedna bez druge,

568
01:19:13,880 --> 01:19:15,560
[SPEAKER_00] a važnija je duhovna.

569
01:19:15,560 --> 01:19:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] I na tome je, ono,

570
01:19:17,279 --> 01:19:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli sukus je na duhovnost.

571
01:19:21,199 --> 01:19:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kak bi mi to argumentirao?

572
01:19:22,260 --> 01:19:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto duhovno?

573
01:19:22,880 --> 01:19:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, zato što se uvijek ideš,

574
01:19:27,720 --> 01:19:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ljubi bližnjeg svog

575
01:19:31,119 --> 01:19:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao samog sebe,

576
01:19:32,119 --> 01:19:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] ono, samaritanac,

577
01:19:40,579 --> 01:19:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] tipa vjera te tvoja spasla,

578
01:19:44,199 --> 01:19:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] to su neke stvari

579
01:19:46,880 --> 01:19:48,479
[SPEAKER_00] koje zajednica

580
01:19:48,479 --> 01:19:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] najviše gleda

581
01:19:50,640 --> 01:19:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] i u tome

582
01:19:51,359 --> 01:19:53,479
[SPEAKER_00] najveću

583
01:19:53,479 --> 01:19:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] i, ajmo reći, pažnju

584
01:19:55,079 --> 01:19:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] daje tome.

585
01:19:56,720 --> 01:19:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, fizički rad

586
01:19:58,119 --> 01:20:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] je bitan

587
01:20:00,159 --> 01:20:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] i rad je sam po sebi dar

588
01:20:03,079 --> 01:20:05,640
[SPEAKER_00] i, mislim,

589
01:20:05,640 --> 01:20:07,100
[SPEAKER_00] mora ga biti,

590
01:20:07,100 --> 01:20:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali da bi mogao

591
01:20:08,199 --> 01:20:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] živjeti,

592
01:20:10,000 --> 01:20:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali, ono,

593
01:20:11,420 --> 01:20:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] Elvira je uvijek

594
01:20:13,119 --> 01:20:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] nas poticala

595
01:20:15,300 --> 01:20:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] da nikada ne

596
01:20:17,619 --> 01:20:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] bježimo

597
01:20:18,819 --> 01:20:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ne skrivamo se

598
01:20:20,260 --> 01:20:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] iza posla, jel?

599
01:20:21,319 --> 01:20:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da se treba

600
01:20:22,840 --> 01:20:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] suočiti sa sobom,

601
01:20:24,680 --> 01:20:25,319
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom,

602
01:20:25,319 --> 01:20:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] treba se Hrvat s Bogom

603
01:20:26,800 --> 01:20:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

604
01:20:28,159 --> 01:20:31,100
[SPEAKER_00] pričat s njim jednostavno,

605
01:20:31,100 --> 01:20:32,060
[SPEAKER_00] iako ti ne ide

606
01:20:32,060 --> 01:20:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] i teško ti je, ono,

607
01:20:33,260 --> 01:20:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] znaš, da ti imaš s njim

608
01:20:34,479 --> 01:20:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] neki dijalog, ono,

609
01:20:36,000 --> 01:20:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] zašto, zbog čega,

610
01:20:37,539 --> 01:20:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] da se imaš pravo se naljutiti

611
01:20:38,960 --> 01:20:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] na nje,

612
01:20:39,220 --> 01:20:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] onaj, to je naš, ono,

613
01:20:40,960 --> 01:20:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] slobodno se naljutiti.

614
01:20:42,460 --> 01:20:45,520
[SPEAKER_01] finno rukavicama,

615
01:20:45,520 --> 01:20:46,840
[SPEAKER_01] pobožne molitve,

616
01:20:46,840 --> 01:20:49,720
[SPEAKER_01] di ti naučene molitve,

617
01:20:49,720 --> 01:20:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] tak neke.

618
01:20:50,220 --> 01:20:51,180
[SPEAKER_01] Cilje je kagod,

619
01:20:51,180 --> 01:20:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] znači, rukama i nogama.

620
01:20:52,380 --> 01:20:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] Rukama i nogama,

621
01:20:53,319 --> 01:20:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] samo da, ono,

622
01:20:54,420 --> 01:20:56,859
[SPEAKER_00] da dođeš do tog trenutka

623
01:20:56,859 --> 01:20:57,680
[SPEAKER_00] da osjetiš to.

624
01:20:57,680 --> 01:20:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bitno,

625
01:20:58,340 --> 01:20:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] ono, na koji način.

626
01:20:59,739 --> 01:21:01,079
[SPEAKER_00] znači, imaš način,

627
01:21:01,079 --> 01:21:04,479
[SPEAKER_00] alat krunica

628
01:21:04,479 --> 01:21:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] i misa.

629
01:21:06,119 --> 01:21:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to,

630
01:21:08,699 --> 01:21:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] imaš sve to pismo

631
01:21:10,000 --> 01:21:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] i,

632
01:21:10,739 --> 01:21:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

633
01:21:12,460 --> 01:21:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako ti to hoćeš,

634
01:21:14,000 --> 01:21:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] tako ti to, ono.

635
01:21:15,079 --> 01:21:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] A, kaj bi sad ti meni rekao da

636
01:21:17,239 --> 01:21:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] tu nas pro tebe sedje neko ko kaže,

637
01:21:20,359 --> 01:21:22,359
[SPEAKER_01] ok, ja konzumiram drogu

638
01:21:22,359 --> 01:21:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] već dugi niz godina,

639
01:21:24,500 --> 01:21:25,100
[SPEAKER_01] međutim,

640
01:21:25,100 --> 01:21:27,279
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam isto tako,

641
01:21:27,279 --> 01:21:27,779
[SPEAKER_01] vjernik,

642
01:21:27,779 --> 01:21:28,680
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga,

643
01:21:28,680 --> 01:21:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] nebitno obratio,

644
01:21:30,260 --> 01:21:31,020
[SPEAKER_01] ne obratio kagod,

645
01:21:31,020 --> 01:21:31,319
[SPEAKER_01] opće,

646
01:21:31,319 --> 01:21:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] ne, ne, ne,

647
01:21:32,119 --> 01:21:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] čak neću reći da podrazumijem

648
01:21:34,380 --> 01:21:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] da vjernik nema problem s drogom,

649
01:21:35,539 --> 01:21:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je jednostavno neka stvar

650
01:21:36,619 --> 01:21:37,479
[SPEAKER_01] u koju možeš upasni,

651
01:21:37,479 --> 01:21:38,520
[SPEAKER_01] opće,

652
01:21:38,520 --> 01:21:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] ne,

653
01:21:39,600 --> 01:21:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] ne želim čak reći da si loša osoba,

654
01:21:41,359 --> 01:21:41,899
[SPEAKER_01] nego jednostavno,

655
01:21:41,899 --> 01:21:42,720
[SPEAKER_01] ok, imaš takav,

656
01:21:42,720 --> 01:21:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] tak se dogodilo.

657
01:21:46,359 --> 01:21:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] I ja,

658
01:21:47,880 --> 01:21:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] i osoba preko puta tebe,

659
01:21:50,260 --> 01:21:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom slučaju ja kaže,

660
01:21:51,300 --> 01:21:51,560
[SPEAKER_01] ok,

661
01:21:51,560 --> 01:21:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne bi ušao

662
01:21:54,340 --> 01:21:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] u zajednicu,

663
01:21:55,840 --> 01:21:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću se samo,

664
01:21:57,680 --> 01:21:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] još ja će molit Bogu.

665
01:21:59,600 --> 01:22:04,100
[SPEAKER_01] To je apsolutno njegovo pravo.

666
01:22:04,100 --> 01:22:07,020
[SPEAKER_01] A kad bi te ja tražio

667
01:22:07,020 --> 01:22:08,680
[SPEAKER_01] tvoje mišljenje na tu moju tezu?

668
01:22:08,680 --> 01:22:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gledaj,

669
01:22:11,119 --> 01:22:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja,

670
01:22:11,420 --> 01:22:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da molitva sigurno može pomoć,

671
01:22:14,859 --> 01:22:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno,

672
01:22:16,279 --> 01:22:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] ili pomogla meni,

673
01:22:18,319 --> 01:22:22,439
[SPEAKER_00] taj odnos s Bogom sigurno može pomoć,

674
01:22:22,439 --> 01:22:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] ili pomogla meni,

675
01:22:24,180 --> 01:22:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] možda mi je više pomogao nego odnos sa

676
01:22:26,800 --> 01:22:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] mojim bližnjima.

677
01:22:31,279 --> 01:22:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] Taj odnos i ta molitva mi je ono,

678
01:22:37,420 --> 01:22:39,060
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao,

679
01:22:39,060 --> 01:22:39,520
[SPEAKER_00] otvorila oči,

680
01:22:39,520 --> 01:22:43,520
[SPEAKER_00] potakla me na neka promišljenja,

681
01:22:45,520 --> 01:22:49,479
[SPEAKER_00] nužno nije da ti moraš biti u ono,

682
01:22:49,479 --> 01:22:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao,

683
01:22:49,979 --> 01:22:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] zatvoren u zajednici

684
01:22:52,300 --> 01:22:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] i da se bez toga ne možeš riješiti.

685
01:22:57,140 --> 01:22:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja samo kažem da je ono,

686
01:22:58,960 --> 01:23:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su dvoje i troje u moj ime,

687
01:23:01,420 --> 01:23:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam ja s njima ide puno lakše,

688
01:23:03,619 --> 01:23:06,640
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam je jako teško,

689
01:23:07,640 --> 01:23:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono,

690
01:23:08,260 --> 01:23:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom nisi sam,

691
01:23:09,500 --> 01:23:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa ono,

692
01:23:10,539 --> 01:23:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno podržavam,

693
01:23:13,199 --> 01:23:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali po meni da je lakše

694
01:23:17,000 --> 01:23:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] i da je možda

695
01:23:18,300 --> 01:23:20,979
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavnije,

696
01:23:20,979 --> 01:23:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] pragmatičnije,

697
01:23:22,340 --> 01:23:24,439
[SPEAKER_00] neću reći brže,

698
01:23:24,640 --> 01:23:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali u nekom kontekstu

699
01:23:27,840 --> 01:23:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] je sigurno da smo ono,

700
01:23:30,659 --> 01:23:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] da si u...

701
01:23:32,600 --> 01:23:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] A to je neki u tabani put,

702
01:23:33,840 --> 01:23:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] bih rekli u stvari,

703
01:23:34,500 --> 01:23:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] da si s nekim

704
01:23:35,800 --> 01:23:36,479
[SPEAKER_00] i da ti on,

705
01:23:36,479 --> 01:23:38,060
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

706
01:23:38,060 --> 01:23:40,479
[SPEAKER_00] da te vodi,

707
01:23:40,479 --> 01:23:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] znači da ti kaže

708
01:23:41,640 --> 01:23:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj ići tu desno,

709
01:23:42,720 --> 01:23:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] idi ljevo,

710
01:23:43,239 --> 01:23:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] znači da ti ta ruku

711
01:23:44,260 --> 01:23:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] kroz šumu

712
01:23:46,819 --> 01:23:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] da te provede,

713
01:23:47,640 --> 01:23:48,319
[SPEAKER_00] mi ono,

714
01:23:48,319 --> 01:23:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

715
01:23:48,800 --> 01:23:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] dosta puta ti ne vidiš

716
01:23:51,039 --> 01:23:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] drva od šume,

717
01:23:53,300 --> 01:23:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

718
01:23:53,880 --> 01:23:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili ono,

719
01:23:55,300 --> 01:23:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] da jednostavno ti neko da,

720
01:23:57,399 --> 01:24:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ti bude to neko svjetlo

721
01:24:00,000 --> 01:24:02,020
[SPEAKER_00] i da te ono vodi,

722
01:24:02,020 --> 01:24:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] znači ali,

723
01:24:02,960 --> 01:24:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] da li čovjek može

724
01:24:04,720 --> 01:24:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] se riješiti toga sam,

725
01:24:06,380 --> 01:24:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] može,

726
01:24:07,699 --> 01:24:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] ja vjerujem da može.

727
01:24:09,279 --> 01:24:10,520
[SPEAKER_01] A dajme reći još samo,

728
01:24:10,520 --> 01:24:11,720
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

729
01:24:11,720 --> 01:24:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] sad si tu spomenuo,

730
01:24:13,600 --> 01:24:15,819
[SPEAKER_01] ti spomenuo da si svaki dan

731
01:24:15,819 --> 01:24:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] imali mislu i...

732
01:24:17,920 --> 01:24:18,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro,

733
01:24:18,180 --> 01:24:20,300
[SPEAKER_01] negdje sam pročituo

734
01:24:20,300 --> 01:24:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] tvojom intervju

735
01:24:22,380 --> 01:24:23,479
[SPEAKER_01] jednom prije koje si dao,

736
01:24:23,840 --> 01:24:24,720
[SPEAKER_01] da je

737
01:24:24,720 --> 01:24:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] najlakša stvar u stvari

738
01:24:26,460 --> 01:24:27,619
[SPEAKER_01] rješiti se te kemijske

739
01:24:27,619 --> 01:24:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] navezanosti,

740
01:24:28,720 --> 01:24:29,100
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

741
01:24:29,100 --> 01:24:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] abstinirati od toga,

742
01:24:30,000 --> 01:24:31,100
[SPEAKER_01] da je puno veći problem

743
01:24:31,100 --> 01:24:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] promijeniti stil života

744
01:24:32,920 --> 01:24:34,399
[SPEAKER_01] i tu naviku,

745
01:24:34,399 --> 01:24:34,680
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

746
01:24:34,680 --> 01:24:35,479
[SPEAKER_01] resetirati sebe.

747
01:24:36,140 --> 01:24:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom se ti imali svaki dan

748
01:24:37,279 --> 01:24:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] misle,

749
01:24:37,579 --> 01:24:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] pretpostavljam svećenike

750
01:24:38,579 --> 01:24:40,479
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan ili...

751
01:24:40,479 --> 01:24:42,560
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zavisi u kojoj si bratošni,

752
01:24:42,560 --> 01:24:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] negdje ono,

753
01:24:43,239 --> 01:24:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] ako si u nekom ono centralnom,

754
01:24:45,159 --> 01:24:46,600
[SPEAKER_00] centralnom bratošni,

755
01:24:46,600 --> 01:24:48,020
[SPEAKER_00] tu su svećenici,

756
01:24:48,020 --> 01:24:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] zajednice,

757
01:24:48,680 --> 01:24:51,439
[SPEAKER_00] zajednica danas ima

758
01:24:51,439 --> 01:24:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] dvanaestak svećenika,

759
01:24:53,119 --> 01:24:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] ima svoj,

760
01:24:54,079 --> 01:24:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] svoj red časnih sestara,

761
01:24:57,159 --> 01:24:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] časnih sestara od uskrsnuća,

762
01:24:58,840 --> 01:25:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] priznata je u crkvi.

763
01:25:00,560 --> 01:25:02,439
[SPEAKER_00] To su sve

764
01:25:02,439 --> 01:25:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] dečki koji su došli,

765
01:25:06,380 --> 01:25:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji i ja,

766
01:25:06,920 --> 01:25:09,100
[SPEAKER_00] i osjetili neki poziv

767
01:25:09,100 --> 01:25:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] i krenuli tim smjerom.

768
01:25:11,300 --> 01:25:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

769
01:25:12,420 --> 01:25:13,899
[SPEAKER_00] to je onako,

770
01:25:13,899 --> 01:25:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] top priča ima

771
01:25:17,819 --> 01:25:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] sa time,

772
01:25:20,319 --> 01:25:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Don Massimo,

773
01:25:21,960 --> 01:25:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Don Stefano,

774
01:25:22,920 --> 01:25:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] Don Andrea,

775
01:25:23,760 --> 01:25:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Don Eugenio,

776
01:25:26,119 --> 01:25:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] to su stvarno,

777
01:25:28,399 --> 01:25:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno ozbiljne priče,

778
01:25:32,380 --> 01:25:35,020
[SPEAKER_00] svaka je na svoj način

779
01:25:35,020 --> 01:25:36,600
[SPEAKER_00] zanimljiva i nevjerovatna,

780
01:25:36,600 --> 01:25:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] a ono,

781
01:25:39,619 --> 01:25:41,520
[SPEAKER_00] veliki ti je dar

782
01:25:41,520 --> 01:25:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad živiš u takvoj nekoj bratoštini,

783
01:25:43,859 --> 01:25:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] svaka bratoština u zajednici je dar,

784
01:25:47,079 --> 01:25:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo,

785
01:25:48,279 --> 01:25:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gdje su svećenici,

786
01:25:50,279 --> 01:25:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] gdje oni žive tu,

787
01:25:51,779 --> 01:25:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] je baš ono,

788
01:25:52,460 --> 01:25:53,600
[SPEAKER_00] imaš,

789
01:25:53,600 --> 01:25:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] možeš razgovarati

790
01:25:55,460 --> 01:25:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] puno,

791
01:25:57,039 --> 01:25:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] možeš

792
01:25:57,960 --> 01:26:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] misa je tu ono,

793
01:26:00,560 --> 01:26:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] svakodnevno,

794
01:26:02,380 --> 01:26:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] biti taj neki suživot s njima je ono,

795
01:26:04,779 --> 01:26:06,979
[SPEAKER_00] ozbiljno dobar i pomaže.

796
01:26:06,979 --> 01:26:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] kad se tiče nekje još stučne pomoći na drugostalno,

797
01:26:09,680 --> 01:26:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] neka psiholog po potrebi.

798
01:26:11,340 --> 01:26:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ba, gledaj,

799
01:26:12,680 --> 01:26:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] danas je to izazovno vrijeme

800
01:26:17,319 --> 01:26:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] i mi moramo ići u korak s vremenom,

801
01:26:19,520 --> 01:26:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] znači ja sam izašli zajednice,

802
01:26:22,119 --> 01:26:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] ušto sam 2007.

803
01:26:23,920 --> 01:26:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] izašli 2011.

804
01:26:25,000 --> 01:26:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] 2011. do 2024.

805
01:26:27,720 --> 01:26:30,479
[SPEAKER_00] puno godina i to se puno,

